task.summary:
added ItemGroup and object that links Items and Groups
Now when getting an item this class will query for groups on top of the item itself but leave the groups items empty to avoid looping. visa versa for getting a group

added EventCall This object has a json field. This is a stringified version of request.data This object is used to temporarily store data that the homelynk will supply.
runs at /event_call contains - id - json - timestamp

Added Day, Graph, Hour and Week
These are all used to find date regarding graphs.
Next step: When a Day or Hour is not found in the database an Insufficient_data_event should be thrown.

Added the processor day and hour objects are now generated when the data is being processed and they don't exist yet.
Created a dummy processor that takes the average temperature of all the temperature events during a specific hour
